[
  {
    "startTime": 1.6,
    "endTime": 3.1,
    "text": "Excuse me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.2,
    "endTime": 4.4,
    "text": "Do you mind?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.5,
    "endTime": 6.0,
    "text": "Everywhere else is full."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.1,
    "endTime": 6.699999999999999,
    "text": "Not at all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.2,
    "endTime": 13.899999999999999,
    "text": "I'm Ron, by the way. Ron Weasley."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.0,
    "endTime": 15.3,
    "text": "I'm Harry. Harry Potter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.7,
    "endTime": 20.0,
    "text": "So... so is it true?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.1,
    "endTime": 21.400000000000002,
    "text": "I mean..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.5,
    "endTime": 23.8,
    "text": "Do you really have the..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.9,
    "endTime": 24.599999999999998,
    "text": "The what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.7,
    "endTime": 26.599999999999998,
    "text": "The scar?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.1,
    "endTime": 27.8,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.0,
    "endTime": 30.6,
    "text": "Wicked."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.3,
    "endTime": 36.099999999999994,
    "text": "Anything off the trolley, dears?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.2,
    "endTime": 43.300000000000004,
    "text": "No, thanks. I'm all set."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.4,
    "endTime": 44.5,
    "text": "We'll take the lot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.1,
    "endTime": 48.800000000000004,
    "text": "Whoa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.2,
    "endTime": 58.300000000000004,
    "text": "Bertie Botts Every Flavour Beans?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.4,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "They mean every flavour."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.6,
    "endTime": 65.1,
    "text": "There's chocolate and peppermint, and there's also..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.2,
    "endTime": 68.0,
    "text": "spinach, liver and tripe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.3,
    "endTime": 72.1,
    "text": "George swore he got a bogey flavoured one once."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.1,
    "endTime": 79.69999999999999,
    "text": "These aren't real frogs, are they?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.2,
    "endTime": 83.3,
    "text": "It's just a spell. Besides, it's the cards you want."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.4,
    "endTime": 86.2,
    "text": "Each pack's got a famous witch or wizard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.1,
    "endTime": 87.69999999999999,
    "text": "I've got about 500 myself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.8,
    "endTime": 91.5,
    "text": "Watch it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.3,
    "endTime": 99.1,
    "text": "Ah, that's rotten luck. They've only got one good jump in them to begin with."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.6,
    "endTime": 102.89999999999999,
    "text": "I've got Dumbledore!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.2,
    "endTime": 104.60000000000001,
    "text": "I've got about 6 of him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.6,
    "endTime": 108.5,
    "text": "Hey, he's gone!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.6,
    "endTime": 112.0,
    "text": "Well you can't expect him to hang around all day, can you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.2,
    "endTime": 115.10000000000001,
    "text": "This is Scabbers, by the way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.2,
    "endTime": 116.60000000000001,
    "text": "Pathetic isn't he?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.7,
    "endTime": 117.9,
    "text": "Just a little bit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.0,
    "endTime": 121.5,
    "text": "Fred gave him a spell to turn him yellow. Want to see?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.6,
    "endTime": 122.19999999999999,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.0,
    "endTime": 134.1,
    "text": "Has anyone seen a toad? A boy named Neville has lost one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.2,
    "endTime": 135.2,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.5,
    "endTime": 138.5,
    "text": "Oh! Are you doing magic? Let's see then."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.0,
    "endTime": 147.5,
    "text": "Sunshine, daisies, butter, mellow, turn this stupid, fat rat yellow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.6,
    "endTime": 153.9,
    "text": "Are you sure that's a real spell?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.2,
    "endTime": 157.1,
    "text": "Well, it's not very good, is it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.2,
    "endTime": 160.2,
    "text": "Of course, I've only tried a few simple ones myself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.3,
    "endTime": 162.0,
    "text": "But they've all worked for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.9,
    "endTime": 167.70000000000002,
    "text": "For example..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.3,
    "endTime": 170.9,
    "text": "Oculus Reparo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.2,
    "endTime": 175.39999999999998,
    "text": "That's better, isn't it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.2,
    "endTime": 181.39999999999998,
    "text": "Holy cricket. You're Harry Potter!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.5,
    "endTime": 183.3,
    "text": "I'm Hermione Granger."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.4,
    "endTime": 185.8,
    "text": "And... you are?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.3,
    "endTime": 188.4,
    "text": "Um... Ron Weasley."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.5,
    "endTime": 189.7,
    "text": "Pleasure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.8,
    "endTime": 191.70000000000002,
    "text": "You two better change into your robes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.0,
    "endTime": 193.5,
    "text": "I expect we'll be arriving soon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.6,
    "endTime": 201.2,
    "text": "You've got dirt on your nose, by the way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.4,
    "endTime": 202.20000000000002,
    "text": "Did you know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.3,
    "endTime": 203.3,
    "text": "Just there."
  }
]